00:10:06.917 --> 00:10:07.677
Me estás mentiendo.

00:10:09.277 --> 00:10:10.797
Todos estás mintiendo a mí

00:10:11.397 --> 00:10:11.917
Lianxin.

00:10:13.837 --> 00:10:14.477
¿Qué pasa?

00:10:15.997 --> 00:10:16.477
Ella

00:10:17.037 --> 00:10:17.917
