00:30:55.757 --> 00:30:57.717
es usted, Lv Beiyi.

00:30:59.917 --> 00:31:01.397
Joven maestro, estás borracho.

00:31:05.557 --> 00:31:06.237
Lv Beiyi,

00:31:06.917 --> 00:31:07.877
crees

00:31:09.357 --> 00:31:10.077
en karma?

